subSubSection.paragraph:
Distribution. Widespread in the Indo-West Pacific Ocean, from East Africa and throughout the Indian Ocean to the Indo-Australian Archipelago and New Caledonia , north to southern Japan . Bathymetric range 7–200 m (
De Bruin et al ., 1995
), commonly collected at depths less than 100 m off Taiwan .
